===============================================================================
            Plugin for connect CopterControl board to simulator.
===============================================================================


---------------------------------------
        Building
---------------------------------------

a) download and install:
    - Qt 4.8
    - MinGW 4.4
b) run:
    qmake
    mingw32-make


---------------------------------------
        Installing
---------------------------------------

a) Copy directory "CopterControl" to simulator's "Plugin" folder.
b) Copy dep\*.dll to simulator's root folder.


---------------------------------------
        Configure plugin
---------------------------------------

CopterControl\cc_plugin.ini

    host, port - hostname or IP address and port of target (server)



---------------------------------------
        Tools
---------------------------------------

udp_test utility can be used for test connection.

	host, port - hostname or IP address of local computer
